Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是椿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.38,0:00:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真少见呢 居然在这种地方不期而遇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦 去买东西了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.81,0:00:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 去买衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约会用的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.01,0:00:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是暑假末了 既然偶遇了就顺便
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.67,0:00:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去哪个店吃个冰淇林如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,0:00:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:00:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.98,0:00:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有啥不好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得同学之间遇上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.89,0:01:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第6话 谜之升级
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 椿的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.79,0:03:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}这家冷饮店的冰淇林很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}诶 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是小学生的身高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有胸部在茁壮成长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这个有点不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙是指
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和丘两人一起吃冰淇林的事被知道的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后会被上野训的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 那个不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿被信任着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公平和我一起的时候经常称赞椿的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然运动神经和成绩都很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本性还是个好家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是称赞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公平?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公平是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是上野的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:04:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丘用名字叫上野的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只是偶尔而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 上野有时也会用名字叫丘你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 会的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.51,0:04:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为叫步子 所以会叫我步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和卜部之间真无法想象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎 怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.18,0:04:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然用名字叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真甜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非椿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才在想象被喜欢的女孩用名字叫的情景吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没在想象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说刚开学的早晨 果然起不来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我差点就没起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果老姐没叫醒我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 浑身乏力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新学期困乏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假啊 还想多要一个月左右呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 昨天有和丘说什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 和丘？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:42.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 昨天没说过话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 什么啊 很让人在意的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:06:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 晒黑了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了海边之类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 算是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.23,0:06:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非你交到女朋友 然后和她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和老姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和老姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 比起和男人一起要好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要你多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我昨天在中央町和椿偶遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 难得遇上了 就两人聊了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聊了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和上野偶尔不用姓而用名去相互称呼的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.92,0:06:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了那个话题之后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿就沉默了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我突然用「明」叫了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他吓到了 然后脸撞到冰淇林上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是在想象被卜部用名字叫的情景吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿果然很让人感兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.46,0:07:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉 热起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才在想象被椿用名字叫你的情景了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 那样的话 为啥我脸会红呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.92,0:07:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红了吧 我的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐呐 卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部 真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真热
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天太阳真毒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍稍去公园休息下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去买果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我买回来…了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要硬叫醒她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果汁买回来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比在学校时睡得更沉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美琴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 我买果汁回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然觉得不用叫醒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是趁果汁还没变温时喝比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫醒我的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:10:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发觉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是是笑脸的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为被叫做「美琴」而高兴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美 美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美 美…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣鸣蝉还在叫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明夏天都结束了 蝉真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 据说鸣鸣蝉在不同的地方叫声会不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中国的鸣鸣蝉不是咪~咪咪咪的叫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是咪咪咪咪~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用名字互称还有点太早了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 今天卜部的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B part
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部是我的女朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让我拍一张卜部的照片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想至少要有一张自己女朋友的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你怎么照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会数 3 2 1 拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦来一张满脸笑容的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.36,0:13:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.99,0:13:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要照的话就这个表情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了拍照而制造笑容是没有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我想要张有笑容的照片…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就没戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微笑一笑也可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部今天好迟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.38,0:14:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是椿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:14:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早川
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:15:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还记得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 毕竟初中三年都是同班
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟椿也都在委员会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都还记得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 椿 如果你不介意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.13,0:15:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在找一家咖啡厅坐坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多令人怀念的事情想说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.02,0:15:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在在等人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该马上就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.78,0:15:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 今天没有空…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 真是遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次有机会再说吧 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢啊 卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道有没有到附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么时候在那里的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看椿聊得很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉不好打搅 就等着了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没愉快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前椿给我看的照片里的女孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿初中的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单恋的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.33,0:16:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.81,0:16:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以也拒绝了她邀请我去咖啡厅的提议…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.67,0:17:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我和早川去了咖啡厅的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.58,0:17:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是打个比方啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是假设
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能会有那种事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把嘴张开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼泪突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果椿抛下我和她去了咖啡厅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然不会生气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想会很伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 现在从椿的眼里所流下的眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是椿比起我反而选择了她的那时 我所流下的眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个… 卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:19:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早川的确是我以前的单恋对象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天难得见面 觉得的确是个美女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拒绝邀请的时候 说实话我的确觉得可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在喜欢的是卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那绝对是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部 保持这个表情不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想把现在卜部的笑容拍下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你愿意让我拍下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会珍惜那张照片的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 卜部 我拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我数3 2 1就拍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.86,0:20:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦来点笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3 2 1 好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.93,0:20:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.33,0:20:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说好的笑容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没有笑容 可这也是我的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 我想要有笑容的照片…
